This cottage has been owned by the same family for six decades. It's now your turn to build some forever memories. Other features include three bedrooms, spacious dining and living room areas, a real wood burning fireplace, large back storage porch and fire pit. This property has a large double sized lot ideal for large family gatherings, BBQ's and evening campfires. Don't miss out on this great cottage!

Welcome to this beautifully renovated 2-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom townhome. This home boasts a tasteful blend of modern updates and cozy charm. Featuring brand new carpet, fresh paint, inviting open floor plan, and in unit washer and Dryer. Enjoy a freshly landscaped patio and BBQ area with privacy wall. Additional conveniences include a designated parking space (#7) and ample guest parking (#s 12-20). Walking distance to Whole Foods, Downtown Bellingham, Whatcom Falls, and more!

This charming 1, 900 sq. ft. Mid-Century rambler offers the perfect mix of peaceful living and convenience, just minutes from Bellingham and Ferndale. Nestled on a large, sun-filled lot (.25 acre), the home features 3 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, and two living rooms, providing ample space for entertaining or relaxation. A versatile bonus room can serve as a home office or gym, while the dedicated laundry room with a separate entrance adds extra convenience. Step outside to enjoy the covered deck, fully fenced backyard, and two large outbuildings for storage or workshop. Recent upgrades include a new septic system, Heat pump with mini-split for year-round comfort. This is the perfect home for those seeking space, comfort, and a prime location!

Located in a beautiful park like setting, Cedar Grove Park is a 55+ and older community. It's close to shopping districts, parks, some with evening concerts and medical services. This 2BD, 2BA, manufactured home was built in 1986. It boasts new flooring. Cedar Grove Park is close to the Lake Padden PGA Golf Course, Lake Padden itself features swimming fishing, boat launch. Tennis and Pickleball courts, biking and hiking trails and a fenced off dog park. You also have access to a beautiful Club House complete with kitchen overlooking a scenic pond. You will feel like you are living in a park-like-setting with all the mature trees throughout the coveted Cedar Grove Park.

Stunning 5-Bed/3.5 home w/ Mt Baker views on 2.24 Acres! This 3, 150 sft. residence features an open & spacious floor plan, perfect for entertaining & everyday living. Enjoy breathtaking view of Mt. Baker from great room, kitchen, & primary bedroom. Plenty of space to spread out. A few of the details on this property incl. a floor-to-ceiling stone F/P, gourmet kitchen w/ custom cabinets & S.S. appliances, a 50 yr roof, 22KW generac whole house generator & a water softener system. Great location nestled at the end of a private road w/ a handful of beautiful homes for ultimate enjoyment. An expansive 30 x 42 shop w/ 2- 12-foot doors w/ an enclosed loft/workspace. Partially fenced, pasture area, patio, fruit trees & so much more. A must see!

If you love living the PNW adventure lifestyle then this 3BR, 1.75BA rambler on a FLAT double lot is waiting for you! Extremely private, this home has plenty of natural light, vaulted living room ceilings, & a double-sided wood fireplace tying together your living and dining spaces. Your kitchen features granite counters, a large island w/storage, + stainless steel appliances. Relax in your spacious primary BR with attached bath, double closets & a private slider to your huge back deck. The oversized garage is ideal for hobby storage which pairs perfectly w/being walking distance to Gate 2 amenities such as AM/PM Beach, the barn/fitness center, pools, & more!

This home is ready for you to move in immediately and continue to live as comfortably as the current owner or update it to make it your own. Located in the desirable Columbia neighborhood close to shopping, Squalicum Creek Park is minutes from popular trails and everything else that Bellingham has to offer! Inside, this well-cared-for three-bedroom, one-bath home has an updated electrical panel and additional third bedroom from its original configuration. It also has a n open living room and kitchen with eating space. Outside, a large covered deck greets your guests. The corner lot offers lots of options for the new owner: like expanding the garage for a shop or an ADU, has a fenced yard, and additional parking for guests or RV.
nearby_schools: Northwest Educational Service District 189, Bellingham Public Schools

text: Located in the sought after SUNNYLAND neighborhood, this beautifully updated 2, 114 square foot, 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home connects historic charm with modern comfort. Built in 1900, this residence features open living and dining spaces, tall ceilings, and a cozy gas fireplace creating a warm atmosphere. Enjoy the remodeled kitchen and baths, plus new siding, and windows for contemporary appeal. The fully fenced backyard boasts a large deck and pergola, perfect for relaxing or entertaining. The detached garage offers extra storage and is wired for EV charging. Just a short stroll from vibrant breweries, restaurants, and Trader Joes, plus views of Mt. Baker and surrounding hills. Dont miss your chance to own a slice of Bellinghams charm!
